dapp.description:
Across V3 is a cross-chain optimistic bridge that uses actors called Relayers to fulfill user transfer requests on the destination chain.

Relayers are later reimbursed by providing a proof of their action to an Optimistic Oracle on Ethereum. Relayer reimbursements over a specific block range are bundled and posted onchain as merkle roots which uniquely identify the set of all repayments and rebalance instructions.

Across V3 is a cross-chain optimistic bridge that uses actors called Relayers to fulfill user transfer requests on the destination chain.

Relayers are later reimbursed by providing a proof of their action to an Optimistic Oracle on Ethereum. Relayer reimbursements over a specific block range are bundled and posted onchain as merkle roots which uniquely identify the set of all repayments and rebalance instructions.

Velodrome Finance, at its core, is a solution for protocols on Optimism to properly incentivize liquidity for their own use cases. Building on top of the groundwork laid out by Solidly, our team has addressed that first iteration's core issues to realize its full potential.
